Package io.curiositycore.thecuriositycore.inventorymenus.handlers

Class InventoryMenu

java.lang.Object
io.curiositycore.thecuriositycore.inventorymenus.handlers.InventoryMenu
All Implemented Interfaces:
InventoryHandler, InventoryMenuHandler
public abstract class InventoryMenu extends Object implements InventoryMenuHandler
Abstract that represents the generalisation of any custom inventory menu within a plugin. This class handles any events that correspond to an inventory menu, and hence bypasses a lot of the Bukkit classes that lead to performance hits.
